Adelani Adepegba, Abuja The United States has handed over 200 ventilators to the Federal Government on Tuesday. This is in fulfillment of the promise made by the US President Donald Trump during a telephone conversation with his Nigerian counterpart, Major General Muhammadu Buhari (retd.) in April 2020. The medical equipment was handed over to the Minister of Health, Dr. Osagie Ehanire, by the US Ambassador to Nigeria, Mary Leonard, at a ceremony in Abuja this morning. Details laterâ€¦